dct_title_s: Property of Mexican Petroleum Corporation showing proposed wharf and dredging, East Rutherford, near Passaic, NJ
dct_description_sm: Map showing property location of the Mexican Petroleum Corporation and the proposed wharf and dredging in relation to the Passaic River
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
This map is second in a group of three stapled together pertaining to the Mexican Petroleum Corporation.
Map undated; date inferred from other maps in collection
